<FONT SIZE=+2><B>AN EYEWITNESS ACCOUNT OF THE SECOND COMING:</B></FONT>
<IMG ALIGN=BOTTOM SRC="turnbo.gif" WIDTH="00037" HEIGHT="00030"></CENTER><BR>
<CENTER><IMG ALIGN=TOP SRC="gospel.gif" ALT="GOSPEL">
<FONT SIZE=-1 COLOR="#FFFFFF">&copy;</FONT></CENTER><P align=justify>
<A HREF="http://www.fdungan.com/sent.htm"><IMG ALIGN=LEFT SRC="cover.png" WIDTH="00157" HEIGHT="00247" ALT="The Gospel According to Condo Don"></A><FONT FACE=arial,helvetica color=black size=4><B>
Two millennia ago, the Son of God promised to return.  In 1984, that promise was fulfilled.  You may have even passed Him on the street and not been aware of it.  Of course, you probably thought you had more important things to do than  look for the Savior.  Now, as you read an eyewitness account of the Second Coming, you realize just how wrong you were.  Don't worry, there is still time.  But I wouldn't delay, because it is your immortal soul that is at stake.  Jesus Christ wants to change your life.  He thinks you are worth saving.  So, why do you keep trying to prove Him wrong? The choice is yours alone.  You can either join the parade or you can stay on the sidelines and watch salvation pass you by.</B></FONT></P>
