<IMG ALIGN=left SRC="bush.gif" WIDTH="00098" HEIGHT="00150" ALT="Bushwhacked"></A><FONT face=arial,tahoma,helvetica size=4 color=lime></DIV><DIV align=justify>There is an ugly dark side to America which you aren't likely to see on television or at the  movies:&nbsp; hungry, out-of-work families being turned away at homeless shelters; flim-flam man Ken Lay bribing Congress to turn its back while Enron fleeces employees and investors alike; the incredibly ridiculous screw-ups that led to 9-11; George W. Bush preaching crass crony capitalism; and Seagrams going all out to get kids to drink.&nbsp;These are topics that won't be discussed on the evening news.&nbsp;Learn what they don't want you to know.</DIV><BR>
